object.script:
function math.loge(num) return math.log(num)/math.log(2.71828) end
function onTick() Water = input.getBool(1) Radar = input.getNumber(1) Baro = input.getNumber(2)
if Water == false then if Radar > 1 then Out = -(math.loge(Radar))-0.5 else Out = -0.5 end end if Water == true then if Baro > 1 then Out = -(math.loge(Baro)) if Baro > 10 then Out = -(math.loge(Baro))-0.5 else Out = -(math.loge(Baro))-0.2 end else Out = -0.2 end end
output.setNumber(1, Out ) output.setBool(1, Water) end
